.TH THEMECTL-VARIANT 1 "2024" "themectl" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
themectl variant \- manage theme variants
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B themectl variant
\fICOMMAND\fR [\fIARGS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage theme variants (dark/light). Variants can be created automatically
or manually edited.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.BR create \fITHEME\fR \fIVARIANT\fR
Create a variant of a theme
.TP
.BR switch \fITHEME\fR \fIVARIANT\fR
Switch to a variant
.TP
.BR list \fITHEME\fR
List available variants for a theme
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-auto
Auto-generate variant instead of prompting (for create command)
.SH EXAMPLES
Create a light variant:
.RS
.PP
themectl variant create gruvbox light --auto
.RE
.PP
Switch to dark variant:
.RS
.PP
themectl variant switch gruvbox dark
.RE
.PP
List variants:
.RS
.PP
themectl variant list gruvbox
.RE
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR themectl (1),
.BR themectl-apply (1)
